Prisma.JsonValue.description:
From https://github.com/sindresorhus/type-fest/
Matches any valid JSON value.

Prisma.JsonObject.description:
From https://github.com/sindresorhus/type-fest/
Matches a JSON object.
This type can be useful to enforce some input to be JSON-compatible or as a super-type to be extended from.

Record_string.string_.description: Construct a type with a set of properties K of type T

Partial_CreateMessagingProfileInput_.description: Make all properties in T optional

Record_string.any_.description: Construct a type with a set of properties K of type T
